1. Naša firma ima preko hiljade* zaposlenih. (Our company has over a thousand employees.) 
2. Grad je prošle godine privukao više od hiljadu* turista. (The city attracted more than a thousand tourists last year.) 
3. Prošle nedelje popio sam hiljadu* kapi vitamina. (I drank a thousand drops of vitamins last week.) 
4. Čuveni pevač ima više od hiljadu* fanova. (The famous singer has more than a thousand fans.) 
5. On je donirao hiljadu* dinara za dobrotvorne svrhe. (He donated a thousand dinars for charitable causes.)